 to England, superseding the native Old English form, <i>Wealdhere</i>. It was a very popular name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Walter de Cantilupe or Cantilou was born in 1050, in Cantelou, Calvados, Lower Normandy, France. He had at least 1 son with Euphamia Cantilupe. He died in 1100, in Normandy, France, at the age of 50."},"et":{"1050–1100":"1050–1100","1055–1138":"1055–1138","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1138":"1138","1100":"1100","1055":"1055","1130":"1130","1050":"1050","1071":"1071","Cantelou, Calvados, Lower Normandy, France":"Cantelou, Calvados, Basse-Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Canteleu, Normandy, France":"Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1050–1100":"1050–1100","1055–1138":"1055–1138","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1138":"1138","1100":"1100","1055":"1055","1130":"1130","1050":"1050","1071":"1071","Cantelou, Calvados, Lower Normandy, France":"Cantelou, Calvados, Basse-Normandie, Ranska","Canteleu, Normandy, France":"Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Ranska","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"1050–1100":"1050–1100","1055–1138":"1055–1138","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1138":"1138","1100":"1100","1055":"1055","1130":"1130","1050":"1050","1071":"1071","Cantelou, Calvados, Lower Normandy, France":"Cantelou, Calvados, Basse-Normandie, France","Canteleu, Normandy, France":"Canteleu, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, France","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Walter de Cantilupe or Cantilou est né en 1050, à Cantelou, Calvados, Basse-Normandie, France. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Euphamia Cantilupe. Il est décédé en 1100, à Normandie, France, à l’âge de 50 ans."},"de":{"1050–1100":"1050–1100","1055–1138":"1055–1138","1071–1130":"1071–1130","1138":"1138"